pullRequest.title: Add the capability to create reports for our license dependencies in backend
pullRequest.bodyText:
Add the capability to create reports for our license dependencies
addresses https://ucsc-cgl.atlassian.net/browse/SEAB-490

commit.message: remove execution download for license plugin
put license plugin in top level pom
make aggregated third party license file and rename
add new third party licenses file
